# Never ship dev tooling output into images
**/node_modules
**/vendor
**/.git
**/.idea
**/.vscode
**/dist
**/test-results
**/android
**/ios
**/*.log
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

# Backend dev artifacts
backend/storage/logs/*
backend/storage/framework/cache/data/*
backend/storage/framework/sessions/*
backend/storage/framework/views/*
backend/storage/framework/testing/*
backend/bootstrap/cache/*.php

# Host env files (compose reads its own)
.env
.env.local
.env.docker

# Repo meta docs that don't belong in the image
**/*.md
!backend/README.md
!frontend/README.md
